@wp.kernel
def expr_odshyf(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = float(0.0)
    v2 = float(1.0)
    tmp = float(0.0)
    v1 = (wp.cos((tmp + 0.22 - v0 + 0.42)) + (v2 - 0.09))
    v1 = (0.28 + ((v2 + 0.03 / v0 + 0.29) / (v0 + 0.78 / v1 + 0.15)))
    v2 = wp.exp(v0)
    v2 = wp.exp((wp.exp(v1 + 0.77) / (v1 + 0.22 - v1 + 0.28)))
    tmp = wp.abs(wp.sin(0.04))
    v0 = (wp.exp((tmp + 0.51 + tmp + 0.1)) + wp.sin(wp.cos(v0 + 0.86)))
    data[tid] = v0
